@DATABASE "Hard Drivin' 128K"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - H - Hard Drivin' 128K"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - H
                   ====================================

                             Hard Drivin' 128K
                             =================


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Time" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(41944,0)"}           41944,0
@{"'Hard Pilot' " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(42478,255)"}           42478,255
@{"Replays = x  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(62941,1)"}           62941,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
